<title>Chihowa yʋt binili ka ƲIT135</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa yʋt binili ka,
 Nana puta kʋt achishke.
 Anukfillit pisa likmʋt,
 A̱hlishke, ahni li hoke.

[V2]
 Yohmi ka chi achukma kʋt,
 Hatak puta chi aiokcha̱ya
 Ish im atahli tuk ak osh
 Isht otʋni ai a̱hlishke.

[V3]
 A̱hli, nanta hak osh yʋmma
 Chohmi na pisa hinla cho?
 Chitokaka holitopa
 Hatak ʋlhtoba kak oke.

[V4]
 Yakni oklushi puta ma!
 Chitokaka aiokpʋchí;
 Enchel puta aiena kʋt
 I̱ shahlichit taloashke.</lyrics>
<author>Captain Joseph Dukes</author>
<hymn_number>135</hymn_number>
</song>